You will
· Perform Continuous Analysis and Requirement Handling
进行持续分析和需求处理
· Develop and Test High Quality Products
开发和测试高质量的产品
· Perform Trouble Shooting and problem solving of sophisticated products
对复杂的产品进行故障排除并解决问题
· Drive Continuous Improvements of Products and Process
推动产品和流程持续改进
· Be a part of multi-functional, self-organizing and highly independent teams
成为多功能、自我组织、高度独立团队中的一员
· Use CI/CD (Continuous Integration/Development) flow and philosophy, with pipelines designed for as-a-Service and to enable DevOps, with fast feedback loops
运用CI/CD（持续集成/开发）流程和理念，结合为即服务而设计的pipelines来实现DevOps，同时具备快速反馈闭环


To be successful in the role you must have
要想在这个职位上取得成功，您必须具备：
· BSc/MSc degree in Computer Science, Telecommunication, or the equivalent level of knowledge
计算机科学、电信或同等知识水平的理学士/理学硕士学位
· Solid Java and C programming skills
熟练的Java和C语言编程技能
· Good knowledge in Packet Core Domain (System solution and network setup)
熟悉数据包核心域（系统解决方案和网络设置）
· Good knowledge in software test and verification concept and methods
熟悉软件测试和验证的概念和方法
· Good knowledge in container and Kubernetes, Kubernetes networking, and package management熟悉container和Kubernetes、Kubernetes网络和数据包管理
· Good knowledge in data structure, e.g. array, list, set, queue, tree, etc.
具有良好的数据结构知识，如数组、列表、集合、队列、树等。
· Experience of software development methods and tools (Object Oriented design, Design pattern, UML)
软件开发方法和工具经验（面向对象设计、设计模式、UML）
· Ability to comprehend IP protocols and IP-based routing, 3GPP standards, UNIX/LINUX is preferred
能够理解IP协议和基于IP的路由，3GPP 标准，UNIX/LINUX者优先考虑
· Good knowledge in Linux network policies for firewall 
熟悉防火墙的Linux网络策略
· To be aware of Lean and Agile principles and be an outstanding teammate
了解精益和敏捷原则，成为一名优秀的团队伙伴


